@startuml seq-17-notification-inbox
title Notification inbox — list, unread, read, delete, attachment

actor "User" as U <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n/notifications" as API <<service>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Storage" as FS <<service>>

note over API: All routes use **authenticateToken**\n(router.use)

B -> API: GET /notifications?page&limit
API -> DB: userNotification.findMany + counts
API --> B: 200 { items, total, unreadCount, … }

B -> API: GET /notifications/unread-count
API -> DB: count where read=false
API --> B: 200 { unreadCount }

B -> API: PATCH /notifications/:id/read
API -> DB: update read=true
API --> B: 200 { ok: true }

B -> API: PATCH /notifications/read-all
API -> DB: updateMany
API --> B: 200 { ok: true }

B -> API: GET /notifications/:notificationId/attachment
API -> DB: find userNotification\nfor user + notification
API -> FS: stream file from attachmentKey
FS --> B: file bytes

B -> API: DELETE /notifications/:id
API -> DB: userNotification.delete
API --> B: 200 { ok: true }

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/notifications.ts**.
end note

@enduml
